	<div class="container">
		<h2>About Glo-Ice <sup>®</sup></h2>
<p>Since 1975, Glo-Ice® has been one of America’s leading lines of buffet serving and display products and Glo-Ice® pieces have graced banquet and buffet tables worldwide for over 40 years.<p>
<p>Wherever there is fine food and buffet service, you can expect to find Glo-Ice® trays, light boxes and related items to enhance visual appeal and ambiance. Glo-Ice® customers include the finest clubs, hotels, restaurants, resorts, catering companies and other hospitality establishments in the US and abroad.</p>
